# Rediant Art Website - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
This is a bilingual (English/Russian) jewelry brand website for Rediant, featuring facechains, headchains, bodychains, and earrings. The site showcases 3D printing technology and artistic jewelry design, hosted on Vercel.

## Current Hosting & URLs
- **Production URL**: https://rediant-art2.vercel.app (temporary)
- **Future URL**: https://rediant.art (once DNS updates)
- **Platform**: Vercel
- **Framework**: Astro 4.x with Tailwind CSS

